functionEntry.name: onShow
functionEntry.documentation: Called when this View is brought to the foreground. Restore the state of this View and prepare it to be shown. This includes loading resources into memory.

functionEntry.name: onHide
functionEntry.documentation: Called when this View is removed from the screen. Save the state of this View here. This includes freeing resources from memory.

functionEntry.name: onUpdate
functionEntry.documentation:
The user has just looked at their watch. Timers and animations may be started here.
Terminate any active timers and prepare for slow updates.
Update the view
